Nokia has unveiled the “most comprehensive line of connected consumer health products in the market”. The announcement coincides with Nokia’s transition of products from the Withings brand to the Nokia name. The new line-up includes digital health products, such as: “The redesigned Nokia Health Mate app (for iOS and Android) functions as the heart of the ecosystem by giving users a 360-degree view of their well-being,” said Nokia. Nokia also detailed new wellness programmes in Health Mate to help users “reach health goals”. The programmes include: 